text: Alberth Villalobos (born 25 January 1995) is a Costa Rican football player who plays for A.D. San Carlos in the Costa Rican Liga FPD. Villalobos made his debut for the senior Costa Rica national football team at the Avaya Stadium on the 2 February 2019 against the United States. ==References== Category:A.D.
